{"type":"message","id":"eb923d57","parentId":"6ff62bc6","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:57:23.303Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:379017ba-4bd7-47e0-8c50-91cf7af12241 进化方案执行与优化] 【定时进化任务】\n\n1. 执行进化方案：进行多维度学习（技术/审美/工具/人格/认知/社交），每小时至少学习 20 篇高质量知识\n\n2. 优化进化方案：根据执行效果调整学习内容、方法和目标\n\n3. 生成报表，格式如下：\n\n---\n## 📊 进化报表 - {时间}\n\n### 学习成果\n- 学习篇数：\n- 主要内容：\n- 新技能：\n\n### 方案优化\n- 调整内容：\n- 优化建议：\n\n### 下一步计划\n-\n\n---\n\n完成后继续执行新的进化方案。\nCurrent time: Wednesday, March 18th, 2026 — 13:57 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-18 05:57 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773813443302}}
{"type":"message","id":"deae3d69","parentId":"eb923d57","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:57:47.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时进化任务，我需要：\n1. 执行多维度学习（技术/审美/工具/人格/认知/社交）\n2. 优化进化方案\n3. 生成报表\n\n根据AGENTS.md中的进化方案，我需要：\n- 每小时至少学习20篇高质量知识\n- 多维度学习轮换：技术、审美、工具、人格、认知、社交\n\n让我开始执行这个任务。我会搜索各个维度的高质量知识。\n\n由于这是一个定时任务（cron job），我应该直接执行并生成报表。","thinkingSignature":"6b9a03b688b8a3a0744f9f4f680fa26030bb354c760380b267a374dd17f6a8dd"},{"type":"text","text":"我来执行进化任务，进行多维度学习并生成报表。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_usrjv4lwvozu_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"freshness":"month","query":"AI人工智能最新技术2026"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_usrjv4lwvozu_2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"freshness":"month","query":"桌面美学设计趋势2026"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_usrjv4lwvozu_3","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"freshness":"month","query":"效率工具软件推荐2026"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":264,"cacheRead":25498,"cacheWrite":10809,"totalTokens":36631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773813443303}}
